metadata.name: PNT23-01 X NADIE
metadata.description:
PANOT FLOR 2023-01 X NADIE
🚶‍♂️
A piece of 2000x2000px paving tile for your Metaverse.
🚶‍♀️
🎨 About the artist:
Nadiecito is an amazing artist who is known for his illustrations which are full of bold lines and playful humor. He puts a unique spin on each character he creates, making his art truly stand out.
😀
His work is filled with clever references to pop culture, funny memes, and striking black-and-white contrasts, making it visually appealing and memorable. His resourcefulness and sharp observations about the world add to the charm of each piece he produces.
😀
In a crowded world of art, Nadiecito's work stands out for its humor, originality, and character design. He has a real talent for line drawings and his work is sure to put a smile on your face.
🚶
Panot lives on the floor of your Metaverse to remind you the importance of keeping your feet on the ground, of growing step by step. Always respecting others.🚶‍♂️WALK-IN🚶
